  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;The proposed first floor side to rear extension, together with the existing gable end roof and poor interaction with the existing rear dormer, would result in an inappropriate roof form which is considered an unduly obtrusive and incongruous addition to the original dwellinghouse which would fail to respect the character and proportions of the dwellinghouse and the visual amenities of the locality and therefore would be contrary to the high quality design aspiration of the National Planning Policy Framework (2023), Policy D3 (D.1 and D.11) of The London Plan (2021), Policies DM1 A, B (a), (b) and (c) of the Development Management Policies Local Plan document (2013) and the relevant provisions of the adopted Harrow Supplementary Planning Document Residential Design Guide (2010).&lt;/p&gt;"
